title: Photo: Liverpool star Nathaniel Clyne meets American rapper
text: Photo: Liverpool star Nathaniel Clyne meets American rapper Wednesday, 21 October 2015 (9 minutes ago) Nathaniel Clyne looks to be a big fan of rap music after the Liverpool defender met American artist Kid Ink on Tuesday night. The England full-back found the energy to head to Manchester to watch the American rapper perform at The 02 Apollo.
